===Noun===
{{en-noun-reg}}

# one who tells [[lie]]s.  Also see "Trent".  noun - large Georgia mammal who is incapable of telling the truth; lacks the ability to discriminate between what is real and what he continually generates in his mind and spews upon his co-workers.  The Trent is believed to be a distant cousin of the Jay-Jay.   
  
